data.description: Welcome HOME!  Remodeled 4 bedroom home on a beautiful level lot that is looking for a buyer to come and finish the final details!  Private street with easy access to shopping and restaurants!  First Floor living with Master and Full bath on first floor with 3 bedrooms on 2nd floor.  New appliances with a GAS stove!! Conveniently located to all major routes, shopping and schools. This freshly finished home offers a fully remodeled kitchen, bright living room and a beautifully updated kitchen. The space boasts updated cabinets, granite counters and new appliances! Rich flooring and warm colored tile finish the spaces. Full bath has been completely remodeled and was designed with comfort in mind.  The very large back yard is perfect for the kiddos furry or not! You don't want to miss out on this one, IT WON"T LAST LONG!
